content_rendered": "<p>在深圳没有人带就废掉了，在深圳就是每天玩游戏哈 每天晚上 11 点 12 点。。。</p>\n<p>目前想了几个方案，儿子绝对不答应 发愁 不知道怎么办</p>\n<ol>\n<li>学习英语 在深圳或老家</li>\n<li>学习游泳或者羽毛球  在深圳或老家</li>\n<li>找个集训的地方 体能训练 在深圳或老家</li>\n<li>找个地方打工  在深圳或者老家</li>\n</ol>\n<p>目前想了几个方案，儿子绝对不答应 发愁 不知道怎么办</p>\n<p>寻求帮忙，</p>\n<p>老家内地四线城市</p>\n", "last_modified": 1719974169, "replies": 119, "id": 1054459}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c74d/97b0/16_large.png?m=1707293361", "name": "share", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c74d/97b0/16_normal.png?m=1707293361", "title": "分享发现", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/share", "topics": 41521, "footer": "", "header": "分享你看到的好玩的，有信息量的，欢迎从这里获取灵感。", "title_alternative": "Share", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c74d/97b0/16_mini.png?m=1707293361", "stars": 5832, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 16, "parent_node_name": "v2ex"}, "member": {"id": 166696, "username": "maowenjie", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/maowenjie", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/6cb3bb8020330d0415f319066ecaa62b?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/6cb3bb8020330d0415f319066ecaa62b?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/6cb3bb8020330d0415f319066ecaa62b?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1459911320, "last_modified": 1459911320}, "last_reply_by": "jasonchen168", "last_touched": 1719997421, "title": "太卷了 女儿中考 553 只能看职高了", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1054341", "created": 1719920892, "deleted": 0, "content": "太心累了", "content_rendered": "<p>太心累了</p>\n", "last_modified": 1719920892, "replies": 94, "id": 1054341}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1650095340", "name": "qna", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1650095340", "title": "问与答", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna", "topics": 220553, "footer": "", "h